query:
SELECT * FROM (
                SELECT
                    event_type,
                    sequence_number,
                    block_hash_bin,
                    block_payload
                FROM dataset_data_blocks
                WHERE dataset_id = $1 AND block_ref_name = $2 AND sequence_number <= $3
                ORDER BY sequence_number DESC
                LIMIT $4
            )
            ORDER BY sequence_number
